Package com.wileyedge.fashiontrendanalysis.model

Class Designer

java.lang.Object
com.wileyedge.fashiontrendanalysis.model.Designer
public class Designer extends Object
Represents a designer in the fashion trend analysis system. Contains information such as designer's name, location, trend count, and popularity score.
